https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flittlenoah.jp%2F&d=5Cz7%2FRjhriApYT0U1Dyvv8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=af7b5148\" target=\"_blank\">https://littlenoah.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻GAME分2個方向<br />\n1. 城鎮  (類似COC) <br />\n起野 攻人搶資源<br />\n<br />\n2. 主線 RAID BOSS 協力<br />\n兵種主要靠以上3種取得<br />\n<br />\nRAID 好睇公會有冇高級boss放出黎，所以盡快入個好既公會好重要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gameapps.hk/images/201412/03/ln1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201412%2F03%2Fln1.jpg&h=64a41621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《&amp;#12522;&amp;#12488;&amp;#12523;&amp;#12494;&amp;#12450;》是一款模擬策略手遊，遊戲模組將採用3D技術繪製而成，目的希望玩家們能夠體驗全新感覺的策略攻防戰！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gameapps.hk/images/201412/03/ln2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201412%2F03%2Fln2.jpg&h=ea2b11c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩家將扮演著一名飛空城的主人，因此需要增強自城戰鬥力，並且進行多方面的討伐來獲得更多的資源來讓飛空城繼續得到發展！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gameapps.hk/images/201412/03/ln3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201412%2F03%2Fln3.jpg&h=2681115c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而遊戲中更支援4人協力系統，讓你跟朋友們不再只是玩單機的攻防戰鬥！順帶一提，本作的角色設定則由吉田明&amp;#24422;設計，遊戲中的音樂則由崎元仁負責，從此可見製作團隊也相當高級呢"},{"pid":"989cbf8a5627234cb29cb9ade59d7f111c4a33c6","tid":3222,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>86快啲過黎同我玩返fgo <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都過左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3533fc8420baf36ecaff2bd33b3244a10099e5e1","tid":3222,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84862a4d05a32ddd60d853929819547f10e672d8","tid":3222,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:31:28.000Z